  schema:description "The author researches the act of ritual dancing - oro - and singing in the posthumous ritual complex, which presents one of the most important ritual and magic activities in order to destroy or neutralize the effects of death, and at the same time, to protect the living members of the social community, as a whole." ;
  schema:author "Љупчо Ристески" ;
